Author: jrms_
Text: Very true. I don't remember anyone at my register except for the dude with coke still stuck in his nose and the lady that bought two bottles of wine a a day. I stopped working there in April

Author: YukiHase
Text: Please don’t fear!!! I work at a grocery store. Everyone is minding their own businesses trying to get their own groceries, and probably aren’t even gonna notice that you’re there. A lot of people move in and out of the store everyday and even if you do get noticed in there they’ll usually forget about it within minutes.
